high_descs: turn around and walk over to the left side of the stove on the right
grab a butter knife off of the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
turn left and walk over to the end of the room
place the knife inside of a glass cup on the upper top counter space
grab the glass cup up off of the counter top
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink on the left
place the cup down inside of the right side sink
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a knife in it inside the kitchen sink on the right

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then turn right to face the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter, to the left of the oven.
Turn left, then go straight to face the counter.
Place the knife in the glass on the counter.
Pick up the glass with the knife in it.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, head past the stove to the counter on the right.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and bring the knife to the glass on the shelf.
Put the knife in the glass on the shelf.
Pick up the glass with knife on the shelf.
Turn around and bring the glass with knife to the sink.
Put the glass with knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn to face the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
Pick up a knife off of the counter
Turn to your left and walk to the kitchen counter ahead of you
Drop the knife into the glass that is on the shelf
Pick up the glass that has the knife in it
Turn around and turn to your left so you are facing the far right of the sink
Drop the glass with the knife in it into the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a glass and put them in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the utensils on the counter top to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife at the back of the counter.
Turn to your left and carry the knife to the counter with the gray glass situated between the spray bottle and the loaf of bread.
Place the knife in the glass, handle first.
Pick up the glass with the knife in it.
Carry the glass to the sink.
Place the glass with the knife in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Carry a glass with a knife in it to the sink
